{"tid":1677751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"海洋公園係最好搞革命嘅地方","createTime":"2019-10-27T09:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T15:56:00.000Z","uid":321318,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3581f7326c5bc5e04ca7f259130fde091c8e16","tid":1677751,"uid":321318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有一班好有心嘅香港人<br />\n係玩嘅同時都不忘光復香港<br />\n有時真係好辛苦佢哋<br />\n要山長水遠去海洋公園抗爭<br />\n又要一邊玩一邊嗌香港人反抗喎</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心我真係唔知你哋要光復同反抗啲乜嘢<br />\n我唔係想割蓆同分化<br />\n但你哋玩嘅同時有冇諗過義士喺入面受緊乜折磨<br />\n冇人話唔俾你哋抖下放鬆下<br />\n但係你哋係咪真係咁需要分享出嚟？<br />\n你哋唔po 啲抗爭同文宣都唔緊要<br />\n都唔好po埋啲吃喝玩樂嘅動態啦<br />\n出到嚟見到都心淡啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己反省下</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rdJYrmd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrdJYrmd.png&h=3ffe5ac1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqy9x1f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhqy9x1f.png&h=d051fee5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c839c2dee9d0f940040be3d49d8be42fa2b8e667","tid":1677751,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"f339c942bfbef2c9e747caef23682556f49b9494","tid":1677751,"uid":53440,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:43:27.000Z","msg":"你咁講自己咪又係有去..<br />\n又要做雞又要拎貞節牌坊<br />\n<br />\n每個人都要放鬆既 但今日應該要去遊行<br />\n不割"},{"pid":"44e99f11e5255d5e1a24a756039c46da2d2e9f88","tid":1677751,"uid":74155,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"又玩苦行分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980b0e1b2d01e85ecf63bbbe7a6660cf406fd9de","tid":1677751,"uid":40407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分化<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"ca93f7c9b4e6a0ed97bd99dd994f96c5ffe233e6","tid":1677751,"uid":321318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f339c942bfbef2c9e747caef23682556f49b9494","tid":1677751,"uid":53440,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:43:27.000Z","msg":"你咁講自己咪又係有去..<br />\n又要做雞又要拎貞節牌坊<br />\n<br />\n每個人都要放鬆既 但今日應該要去遊行<br />\n不割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">只係係ig睇到</span>"},{"pid":"6ce04e8a5a1756b3557c70dfdc59d465a1937e57","tid":1677751,"uid":321318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44e99f11e5255d5e1a24a756039c46da2d2e9f88","tid":1677751,"uid":74155,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"又玩苦行分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"叫平衡時空嘅佢哋清醒下都算分化？<br />\n一個咁簡單嘅動作佢哋都做唔到？"},{"pid":"620643a7e745b3bfaa36a9947bbcffba8a908386","tid":1677751,"uid":239130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"同意樓主<br />\n今日聽到好撚多人玩緊嘅時候大嗌口號真係好心涼<br />\n見住佢哋大路開心玩一路嗌口號感覺好似當嗌口號當玩咁<br />\n我今日都做咗港豬  我對唔住大家但都希望大家明白應該係咩時候做啲咩嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n休息係可以但唔好消費咗之前同依家係尖沙咀抗爭緊嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n今日我無權嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住大家"},{"pid":"7d59755131de4b1246d8f86458df8f92699cca52","tid":1677751,"uid":204726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LhDd0j6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhDd0j6.png&h=26eb69e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76921130e3bd9bb8f6dc3b293c6d43c42623f5b6","tid":1677751,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"620643a7e745b3bfaa36a9947bbcffba8a908386","tid":1677751,"uid":239130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"同意樓主<br />\n今日聽到好撚多人玩緊嘅時候大嗌口號真係好心涼<br />\n見住佢哋大路開心玩一路嗌口號感覺好似當嗌口號當玩咁<br />\n我今日都做咗港豬  我對唔住大家但都希望大家明白應該係咩時候做啲咩嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n休息係可以但唔好消費咗之前同依家係尖沙咀抗爭緊嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n今日我無權嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住大家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"我用咗嚟宣傳11.2同11.3<br />\n在場好多嗌口號嘅都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f004a3bdb1a2d0412a5633afc0bba091477fa7d1","tid":1677751,"uid":110656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"老老實實 閒日或無遊行的日子入去嗌到拆天無咩所謂 好多員工都黃到出面<br />\n但有遊行日子去玩仲要勁開心咁嗌到拆天 其實啲員工都會忍唔撚住暗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552c58b3aa97e480e6a4e87e006f12c9d12802bf","tid":1677751,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b136b870170cde8565185aefabb25d50248d6ad1","tid":1677751,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"Sir"},{"pid":"150dea9d3b760edeed4528ee89781b96278e592c","tid":1677751,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uObc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a6a9a3e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uObc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=32415f90\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uObc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=ade8cb8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"}]}